there was a half deflated bright purple balloon sitting in the middle of the sidewalk  the dog  vigilant as always  approached this alien being object spaceship slowly and warily  ready to pounce if it made any trouble  up close  she inspected it carefully a few moments  jumping back once when it bounced a little after being nudged  when she realized it was harmless  she took a long piss on the helpless depressed thing  as if to tell the world of dogs or any others that might pass by in the future    don   t worry about this         it won   t give you any trouble    author     jonathancarroll comhome to some of the best stories on medium  look around  relax and enjoy one with a sip of coffee 